@startuml export_graph_pdf

' Component definitions
participant "Business User" as User
participant "ExportUI\n(Templates with export\nfunctionality)" as ExportUI

' Sequence flow
User -> ExportUI: Click export button\n(on network graph page)
activate ExportUI

ExportUI -> ExportUI: Trigger export function\nin JavaScript
activate ExportUI
note right: Captures current graph state\nand visualization
deactivate ExportUI

ExportUI -> ExportUI: Generate export file\n(PDF or PNG)
activate ExportUI
note right: Uses canvas or SVG rendering\nto create static image\nof current graph
deactivate ExportUI

ExportUI -> ExportUI: Prepare download
activate ExportUI
note right: Creates blob/data URL\nfor file download
deactivate ExportUI

ExportUI --> User: Download file to device\n(graph_export.pdf or graph_export.png)
deactivate ExportUI

@enduml
